{"tid":2200471,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"度體脂率","createTime":"2020-09-13T04:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T04:57:45.000Z","uid":55737,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b58653b7d36bef84fb9062eec46398230c2f0038","tid":2200471,"uid":55737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:01:23.000Z","msg":"經常覺得屋企個小米磅度體脂率唔準<br />\n上網搵到啲公式計<br />\n但唔知準唔準<br />\n<br />\n體脂肪率 = (BMI x 1.2) + (年齡 x 0.23) &ndash; 5.4 &ndash; (性別 x 10.8)<br />\n其中男性性別為1，女性為0。BMI 則為 體重(公斤) / 身高 (m2)<br />\n<br />\n有冇更好既方式在家中都度到體脂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70334b5dd46490dcf64bec5f2674b3f165e80ce1","tid":2200471,"uid":55737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:03:51.000Z","msg":"仲想問一個月減幾多體脂率為之正常速度"},{"pid":"a7b1a7dea9e3e5bf9b3bfc3ed41aab257b8f9eb6","tid":2200471,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"唔準<br />\n相同BMI既人可以一個人體脂高 一個人體脂低"},{"pid":"4bfa2561314866543bc58b316ce63013fb906d04","tid":2200471,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"冇理過咩body fat都冇理bmi<br />\n睇開肚腩平唔平 肚有凸起就減"},{"pid":"0d63cef62b13f6ea3b18b751286bec773f5a23b9","tid":2200471,"uid":236002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b58653b7d36bef84fb9062eec46398230c2f0038","tid":2200471,"uid":55737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:01:23.000Z","msg":"經常覺得屋企個小米磅度體脂率唔準<br />\n上網搵到啲公式計<br />\n但唔知準唔準<br />\n<br />\n體脂肪率 = (BMI x 1.2) + (年齡 x 0.23) &ndash; 5.4 &ndash; (性別 x 10.8)<br />\n其中男性性別為1，女性為0。BMI 則為 體重(公斤) / 身高 (m2)<br />\n<br />\n有冇更好既方式在家中都度到體脂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:14:00.000Z","msg":"相呢 我隻眼睇就最準"},{"pid":"6313c73b6d85145497a841efd00283b6d7132e86","tid":2200471,"uid":236002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70334b5dd46490dcf64bec5f2674b3f165e80ce1","